      • dequeue

        public void dequeue(boolean all)
        Dequeue Search Calls
        Parameters:
        all - if true then it will dequeue all pending requests by calling the interface's callback method OnSearchResultListener.onRequestCancel(Params, long) , and in case of false it will only cancel the most recent request

      • cancelPendingRequests

        public void cancelPendingRequests()
        To cancel all pending requests. When invoked and there are some pending requests, you will get callbacks for all those pending requests in interface method OnSearchResultListener.onRequestCancel(Params, long) only when the listener is registered through setSearchResultListener(OnSearchResultListener)
